pageContext.claim: “We were spending 85 percent of the money and, frankly, good for everybody, but it helps them a lot more than it helps us. Helps Europe a lot more than it helps us.”
pageContext.analysis: The U.S. does contribute the largest share to NATO, but in 2017, that meant the U.S. contributed 22 percent of NATO funding — a far cry from the 85 percent Trump suggests.
